{"name": "odoo-addon-shopinvader-search-engine-product-media", "metadata": {"name": "odoo-addon-shopinvader-search-engine-product-media", "version": "16.0.1.0.4", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 3 - Alpha", "Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 16.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo-addon-fs-product-multi-media", "odoo-addon-shopinvader-product", "odoo-addon-shopinvader-search-engine", "odoo"], "summary": "Index storage media data into search engine", "upload_time": 1711021903}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Alpha-red.png\n    :alt: Alpha\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-shopinvader%2Fodoo--shopinvader-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader\n    :target: https://github.com/shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader/tree/16.0/shopinvader_search_engine_product_media\n    ```\n---\n\n# Shopinvader Search Engine Product Media\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:3198ddee64d376fa3457c980b9e9b57d618c36bee125ee7c8e13f74e4dba123e\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }}\n\nThis module adds information related to media linked to a product into the\nJSON data exported for a product in a search engine index.\n\n:::{IMPORTANT}\nThis is an alpha version, the data model and design can change at any time without warning.\nOnly for development or testing purpose, do not use in production.\n[More details on development status](https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status)\n:::\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nWhen exporting a reference to a media into your search engine, you can choose\non the search engine backend from where the media will be available.\n(Odoo or External file system)\n\nTo make your media stored outside of Odoo, you need to add and/or configure\na file system storage backend provided by the module [fs_storage] to be used to\nstore files defined on the *Product Media* model.\n\n## Changelog\n\n### 16.0.1.0.4 (2024-03-21)\n\n**Bugfixes**\n\n- Allows to configure the strategy to apply to generate the url for a given media\n  from the search engine backend form view. The field was declared on the model\n  but not displayed on the form. This change adds the field to the form view. ([#1518](https://github.com/shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader/issues/1518))\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader/issues/new?body=module:%20shopinvader_search_engine_product_media%0Aversion:%2016.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Akretion\n- ACSONE SA/NV\n\n### Contributors\n\n- S\u00e9bastien BEAU \\<<mailto:sebastien.beau@akretion.com>>\n- Marie LEJEUNE \\<<mailto:marie.lejeune@acsone.eu>>\n- Laurent Mignon \\<<mailto:laurent.mignon@acsone.eu>>\n\n### Other credits\n\nThe development of this module has been financially supported by:\n\n- Akretion R&D\n- Adaptoo\n- Acsone\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is part of the [shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader](https://github.com/shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader/tree/16.0/shopinvader_search_engine_product_media) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute.\n\n[fs_storage]: https://github.com/OCA/storage/tree/16.0/fs_storage\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_search_engine_product_media.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_search_engine_product_media.models.se_backend", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_search_engine_product_media.models..se_backend", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_search_engine_product_media.tests", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_search_engine_product_media.tests.test_shopinvader_search_engine_media", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_search_engine_product_media.tests..test_shopinvader_search_engine_media", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_search_engine_product_media.models.se_backend", "documentation": ["Copyright 2023 ACSONE SA/NV", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_search_engine_product_media.models.se_backend.CDN_HELP_TEXT", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_search_engine_product_media.models.se_backend.SeBackend", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_search_engine_product_media.models.se_backend.SeBackend._get_url_for_media", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "media", "type": {"name": "FSFile", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.fs_file.fields.FSFile", "project": null}, "params": nul